{"tid":859822,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自從將社交減到最少之後，生活過得爽咗好多","createTime":"2018-10-12T23:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T12:57:40.000Z","uid":79927,"like":146,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2bde3d952815656d6e7641699fb752e15469fda8","tid":859822,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有個星期日訓完晏教<br />\n忽然覺得一陣間夜晚又要出街同一大班人食飯真係好攰<br />\n出到黎啲話題黎黎去去都係個啲，飲飲食食呀無聊是非呀去邊度旅行呀<br />\n其實自己對依啲野都冇乜興趣，但出到黎食飯又要扮到自己對依啲野好有興趣咁<br />\n而一大班人，話題又好難擴展到其他野<br />\n所以咁樣嘅飯局其實我一啲都唔鐘意<br />\n再加上第二朝又要早起身返工，出街食完飯返到屋企都十一二點，沖埋涼搞得依樣個樣黎除時一兩點先訓教<br />\n出黎社交做戲已經夠攰，第二朝要早起但夜訓就更加攰<br />\n係屋企上下連登休息下好似仲舒服仲開心<br />\n於是我就決定放飛機唔出去同人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二朝起身個陣非常精神，令我覺得琴晚嘅決定非常正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我只要有時間就會去啲飯局，無論自己鐘意與否<br />\n但個次一開咗個先例之後，之後多過四個人嘅飯局我都會推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁樣，我諗我推咗之後超過八成嘅飯局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢又洗少咗一截，又多咗時間可以做啲自己想做嘅野<br />\n而最重要嘅係個人亦都開心咗精神咗<br />\n起馬唔洗明明對啲吃喝玩樂是是非非話題一啲興趣都冇但又要扮到好有興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起馬唔會因為出去食飯而搞到明明第二朝勁早要返工都要夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b500afb93fc04ce051d661725756f99c73357a","tid":859822,"uid":54597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T23:45:06.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"0260c8ee3d413fba5480ba80aa071ead4831b7bc","tid":859822,"uid":53122,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T23:49:32.000Z","msg":"d豬朋狗友鳩吹真係無用<br />\n<br />\n得閒自己做gym進修好過"},{"pid":"b046cd6854f68d588adc67219075cec2c0f07310","tid":859822,"uid":79927,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0260c8ee3d413fba5480ba80aa071ead4831b7bc","tid":859822,"uid":53122,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T23:49:32.000Z","msg":"d豬朋狗友鳩吹真係無用<br />\n<br />\n得閒自己做gym進修好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T23:57:46.000Z","msg":"上下連登睇下膠Post笑下好似都比同豬朋狗友鳩吹有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8dbc468046e4752aff438db5d1f22d606a1da5","tid":859822,"uid":10905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T00:06:21.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己鳩流流仲開心過成班人圍威喂"},{"pid":"ad14e4e7e81b46f82c984b235d7943f96b9619ff","tid":859822,"uid":73241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T00:08:52.000Z","msg":"寧願同幾個最close朋友深度傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d90e5ab68c80f827e3d44c1defc7bd0098b954","tid":859822,"uid":79927,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ad14e4e7e81b46f82c984b235d7943f96b9619ff","tid":859822,"uid":73241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T00:08:52.000Z","msg":"寧願同幾個最close朋友深度傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"就算唔深度本身唔Close<br />\n人少少嘅話都易啲傾到多啲飲飲食食是是非非以外嘅話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8732b5d81a6a247e6ec58c0d82700d48224fed","tid":859822,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"536a83689e6cf67afeb50556eb51d2793484e8ed","tid":859822,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"愈來愈累"},{"pid":"623238d27d25d01b48aa85b8e8c01c90f5e113af","tid":859822,"uid":24596,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"62d90e5ab68c80f827e3d44c1defc7bd0098b954","tid":859822,"uid":79927,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ad14e4e7e81b46f82c984b235d7943f96b9619ff","tid":859822,"uid":73